小样本
训练：
python ./train.py ./configs/thumos_i3d_small.yaml --output reproduce
查看训练：
tensorboard --logdir=./ckpt/thumos_i3d_reproduce/logs
评估：
python ./eval.py ./configs/thumos_i3d_small.yaml ./ckpt/thumos_i3d_small_reproduce


所有样本
python ./train.py ./configs/thumos_i3d.yaml --output reproduce
查看训练：
tensorboard --logdir=./ckpt/thumos_i3d_reproduce/logs
评估：
python ./eval.py ./configs/thumos_i3d.yaml ./ckpt/thumos_i3d_reproduce





--带有最优模型保存逻辑的训练脚本
python ./train_best.py ./configs/thumos_i3d_small.yaml --output reproduce

--评估
python ./eval.py ./configs/thumos_i3d_small.yaml ./ckpt/thumos_i3d_small_reproduce